% Failed :assign by precondition (3) typing (BETA1 spec section 3.2.2).
% At a debug prompt the user requests `:assign ?X := nil.` but the
% query gives X the inferred type `nat` while `nil` has type
% `list ?t`. The pipeline that compiles the synthetic `?- X = nil.`
% rejects it during type checking with `*** tc-error[loc]:` before
